{"tid":2499668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子與比特犬同床睡，半夜被狗瘋狂攻擊致死…妻子：狗平時很溫和的…","createTime":"2021-04-22T05:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:25:54.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3550840f678420d37baa07f80d37a55a0be6e9","tid":2499668,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"前兩天4月15日淩晨，泰國春武裏府邦拉蒙區一處民宅中發生慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n56歲男子Wisit在家中熟睡時，突然遭到同床共枕的比特犬攻擊，現場慘不忍睹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf8xbSLNPW1sqDdLoJB9N7PA1nUVzsYsiYduRmXwkQoag?filename=dWmma9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWmma9g.jpg&h=ff12837f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肇事狗Giant今年2歲，在只有3個月大時就來到這個家裏。<br />\n<br />\n主人Wisit總共養了三四只狗，<br />\n<br />\n當時他從朋友那邊以高價買來Giant，平時悉心照顧將其一手帶大。<br />\n<br />\n可以說Wisit愛狗甚至超過了愛妻子，連每天晚上睡覺時都是和狗同處一室。<br />\n<br />\n4月15日事發那天，Wisit和往常一樣打着地鋪，身邊有狗子Giant的陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n然而正當Wisit處于睡夢中時，卻突然遭到了狗子猛烈暴擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb2QKzbc3PLR9i4X4JSDqdEKeVhoMAS24furFBku6YQmt?filename=GdiWKur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdiWKur.jpg&h=69e52b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗子直接咬向Wisit的脖子、頭部等部位，很快地上就流了滿地鮮血。<br />\n<br />\n而狗子似乎興奮得停不下來，咬着朝夕相處的主人死死不放。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQXe9pZW116dyTVtVqoEygXDRNFpHuwYbz4RmnXbuGRrQ?filename=BuebynS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBuebynS.jpg&h=afaf7cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽到奇怪聲響後，Wisit的兒子過來確認情況，看到現場的慘狀後，他頓時驚呆了。<br />\n<br />\n但是看着凶猛的狗子，他一個人也不敢輕舉妄動。<br />\n<br />\n在衆人的努力下，費勁一番功夫後，總算是將身受重傷的Wisit給救了出來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW4AsrWyp1Ck4gocvmNeCyJeDnvpqMozLakvDGT7vrH9A?filename=ggo7Q9F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fggo7Q9F.jpg&h=af0fb044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而凶猛的狗子Giant依然被鐵鏈拴在事發現場，沒人敢去招惹它。<br />\n<br />\n等到專業人士趕到現場後，借助麻醉飛鏢才使得狗子Giant安靜下來。<br />\n<br />\n受害人Wisit身上多處受傷，脖子上有很深的傷口，右耳撕裂，頭皮也被咬破，因為失血過多失去了意識，隨後被救護車緊急送往醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，受害人的妻子Wanpen前些天也被愛犬咬傷，頭上縫了幾針。<br />\n<br />\n不過她還是為愛犬辯護，稱肇事狗Giant平時很溫和，不是外界說的那種惡犬：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我的丈夫非常愛狗，是他將Giant一手養大。<br />\n<br />\n丈夫比我還愛狗狗，身邊的朋友們也同樣愛着它們。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT1UzmFZRHF8SPzMp2E9DRu9uZsPsex8zHcqAqFJJoBW1?filename=KkWEHgx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKkWEHgx.jpg&h=97233a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受害人的兒子也表示，<br />\n<br />\n肇事狗Giant平時個性溫和，這次暴走可能是和天氣悶熱有關，再加上最近比較少帶它出去散步，才會一時心情煩躁襲擊主人。<br />\n<br />\n事發後第二天，4月16日中午時分，<br />\n<br />\n妻子Wanpen打來電話向記者透露，其丈夫經搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n親屬們接到消息後，已經陸續趕往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n至于肇事狗Giant，目前並沒有被處以安樂死。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，它在數百公裏之外的地方找到了新家。<br />\n<br />\n37歲的新主人Suksa Ketnak，在自家別墅的院子裏養了另外4只狗。<br />\n<br />\n盡管發生了致人死亡的悲劇，他還是想給Giant留一條活路。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd7VbdpcTafexFbFFGj7Quqe4Pt1tUocdmdHTX7x11be3?filename=XeBpToj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeBpToj.jpg&h=0244a796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGiant來到新家後，一時提不起情緒，沒有胃口進食。<br />\n<br />\n新主人Suksa覺得，等到Giant適應新的環境後，一切就會恢複正常了。<br />\n<br />\n不過他也是樂觀中帶着謹慎，最近都有密切關注Giant的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n單從這兩天看來，Giant暫時還沒有表現出攻擊性，在和新主人玩耍時沒有出現狂暴的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc6mj8qp553kKrUA879QcC2chuyEtKEBbDq5dWWkMYEMp?filename=gkfBKu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkfBKu7.jpg&h=4fb9bda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有了血的教訓在前，居然還敢收養肇事狗，<br />\n<br />\n要說這新主人，也真是心大啊&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b1d0f6e23c9ec63efa275a5e8987756df009a852","tid":2499668,"uid":367723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"除咗抵死都唔知講乜"},{"pid":"670949b2240fec438318298e03c83c25f98339ce","tid":2499668,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">無一個狗主係無辜</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c5dec4893ca985b1d32ee8dca84575b154e06b2","tid":2499668,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d0f6e23c9ec63efa275a5e8987756df009a852","tid":2499668,"uid":367723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"除咗抵死都唔知講乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"殺左人都可以唔洗人道毁滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31acc245c593acb79243a9b7bd4ead313bfd89c","tid":2499668,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"幾時咬死埋下面嗰個傻鳩新主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053553014a3658948629e34c60a3b6f7805f7ee0","tid":2499668,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"「新主人Suksa覺得，等到Giant適應新的環境後，一切就會恢複正常了。」<br />\n等佢適應之後，就會好正常咁咬死你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e31acc245c593acb79243a9b7bd4ead313bfd89c","tid":2499668,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"幾時咬死埋下面嗰個傻鳩新主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}